title: CDM WG : Pregnancy
body: The Pregnancy and Maternal Medicine working group will present.

title: CDM WG Meeting : NLP
body: The NLP working group will present some potential updates to the NOTE_NLP table.

title: CDM WG Vocabulary Discussion
body: Anna Ostropolets will join to ask us about our experiences using the OMOP Standard Vocabulary for ETL and other purposes

title: CDM WG : HADES
body: Martijn Schuemie will present about the HADES working group and how their work interconnects with the OMOP CDM

title: CDM WG : Medical Imaging
body: Paul Nagy will talk to us about the modeling work being done in the Medical Imaging working group

title: CDM WG : GIS
body: The GIS working group will join us to share what they are working on and how we might support them.
